<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style nonce="<%= nonce %>">
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #3c229c, #f8f9fa);
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: #007bff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
        .faq-section {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .faq-section h4 {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .faq-section p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Our Application</h1>
        <p class="lead">Get started by exploring our features or login to your account.</p>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login</a>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h2>
            <div>
                <h4>What is this application about?</h4>
                <p>This application allows users to manage files securely, including uploading and downloading files. It also features user authentication for secure access.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4>How do I sign up?</h4>
                <p>Click on the "Sign Up" button above to create a new account. You will need to provide some basic information to register.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4>How do I login?</h4>
                <p>If you already have an account, click on the "Login" button to access your account. Enter your username and password to log in.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4>How can I contact support?</h4>
                <p>If you need assistance, please contact our support team via the contact form available in the application or email us directly at support@example.com.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">Login</a>
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
    <!-- Bootstrap Bundle JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
